26.title: YSOON Objectives
26.content: Ysoon was started by a couple of normal people who felt the information being collected unknown had spun completely out of control. It’s time to take back our information. Out of this passion and repeated eye opening events YSOON was born. You Should Opt Out Now . Data Collection . Our main goal is to shine light on the inner workings of those behind the curtains collecting and selling our data, as well as providing a path to opting out. Digital Security . Second on our list is digital security, or how do we keep all of our intimate data safe in this hostile environment.
